                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>teacher of the above school, but also<lb/> as a contribution to orthodox\n                journals<lb/> on religious questions and matters be<lb/> of salutary influence.</p>\n            <p>Hoping you will comply with my<lb/> request and wishing you <add>כוח\"ט כתיבה וחתימה\n                    טובה</add> with<lb/> all my heart, I am, Rev. Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">yours most obediently</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">L. Buttenwieser</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>My direction is:</p>\n            <p><persName role=\"author\">L. Buttenwieser</persName>,</p>\n            <p>care of <persName>Messrs Heller Bros &amp; Co.</persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <placeName>Cincinnati O.</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
